<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She is the former model and radio host who always puts on a fashionable display.</p>

<p>And Kelly Brook was at it again on Friday as she donned a chic patterned wrap dress while arriving to present her Heart FM show at London's Global studios.</p>

<p>The presenter, 40, flashed her pins in her billowing autumnal gown as she made a very stylish entrance ahead of her drive time radio show. </p>

<p>Fabulous: Kelly Brook donned a chic patterned wrap dress while arriving to present her Heart FM show at London's Global studios on Friday</p>

<p>As summer begins to fade, Kelly was sure to dress accordingly for the new season, layering a black jumper beneath her gown.</p>

<p>She accessorised her look with a tan fedora hat and kept warm with a smart pair of black ankle books.</p>

<p>The media personality completed her ensemble with a pretty gold pendant, while she carried her accessories in a black quilted handbag.</p>

<p>Kelly appeared in high spirits as she flashed a broad smile while making her way down the street. </p>

<p>Fashionista: The presenter, 40, flashed her pins in her billowing autumnal gown as she made a very stylish entrance ahead of her drive time radio show</p>

<p>Kelly's stylish display comes as she admitted she's 'not worried' about her 'weight creeping up'.</p>

<p>She also declared 'diets shouldn't be about deprivation', after revealing she shed a whopping two stone in March.</p>

<p>While she has been keeping busy by exercising at home, her diet consists of 'healthy, low-calorie meals' with sweet treats such as popcorn and homemade fruit lollies.</p>

<p>Cosy look: As summer begins to fade, Kelly was sure to dress accordingly for the new season, layering a black jumper beneath her gown</p>

<p>So chic: She accessorised her look with a tan fedora hat and kept warm with a smart pair of black ankle books</p>

<p>The brunette beauty has been candid about her weight fluctuating, with the bombshell slimming down to a size 10-12 after going to a size 16.</p>

<p>On her current figure, she told new! magazine: 'I'm a real foodie and enjoy cooking. I wasn't surprised at all to see my weight creep up a little over the last few weeks.</p>

<p>'[I've gained] a few pounds, but I'm not worried. I know I can lean on the SlimFast 3.2.1. Plan to deal with my weight loss ups and downs, so I can get back on track.</p>

<p>'It's easy and it works. Diets shouldn't be about deprivation - they need to be sustainable after all.'</p>

<p>Looking good: Kelly's fashionable outfit looked good from all angles as she headed into work</p>
